This file is a placeholder so SwiftPM has something to copy as a resource.
Drop a real `bonsai-7k.glb` next to this file and rename it
`bonsai-7k.glb` to enable on-device rendering.

The asset is too large to vendor into git. Download from:
  https://catetus.com/fixtures/bonsai-7k.glb   # public, MIT-licensed
